      "value": "<p><em><strong>Teras Kasi Order:</strong> 17th level</em></p>\n<p>You have learned to harness your strikes in a blistering fury. On your turn, when a creature takes damage from you three times, you can make up to three additional unarmed strikes against the creature (no action required). The first additional unarmed strike costs 1 focus point and deals [[/r 1d12]] additional psychic damage on a hit, and each unarmed strike after the first costs 1 additional focus point and deals [[/r 1d12]] additional psychic damage on a hit, cumulatively.</p>",
